<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - NGC Corp rated a buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - NGC Corp rated a buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Rauscher Pierce Refsnes said it intiated coverage of NGC Corp with a buy-focus rating, saying a recent decline in the stock reresented an excellent buying opportunity.</p>
<p>-- The stock rose 1/2 to 16-1/4.</p>
